723494f-a.title: Manhattan: Sylvan Terrace - St. Nicholas Avenue
723494f-a.text:
Sylvan Terrace, east from St. Nicholas Avenue. This is a one block cobbled stoned mews street which extends to Roger Morris Park, where the white Morris Jumel Mansion can be seen.
E. P. Chrystie  May o, 1923
Revised Felicia de Chabris May 21, 2015
